Timokhovo will produce 72.5 million kilowatt-hours and will continue to operate as a waste recycling complex.
And at the Balashikha training ground "Kuchino", which was closed after residents complained about the "Direct Line" with the president of the country, a museum can be created.
"There was such an idea - to create a museum of reclamation of landfills of the Moscow region," - said Deputy Prime Minister - Minister of Ecology and Nature Management of the region Dmitry Kurakin.
